text.tspan: Make me a man of light with my eyes set on Thee
Remove the many veils that are now cov’ring me,
My heart I turn, O Lord—Spirit come and set me free!
That deeper mingling Thou would’st make;
Oh, may Thy life grow more today
Until Thy life fills all my ways.
When to Thy word I come, help me to contact Thee,
Be present, dear and fresh—let Thy speaking water me;
Oh, may my spirit, Spirit strike,
Thy Holy Word, a flame, ignite!
Thy present word to me make clear;
Thy secret things, Lord, I would hear.
